THE FIRST TAKE

THE FIRST TAKE
IT ONLY HAPPENS ONCE.

Episode 624 features singer-songwriter Lilas.
She will perform “Koikaze ,” a song she created as the theme song for the ABEMA romance reality show, “Kyo Sukini Narimashita” (translated as: I Fell In Love Today) , released in April 2025. The track delicately portrays the gentle emotions that arise when falling in love, as well as the tender feelings one holds for the other.
Enjoy Lilas's one-shot performance of a refreshing song that evokes approaching spring, accompanied by marasy, a pianist with over 2 million YouTube followers, in an original piano-and-vocal rendition that showcases both of their strengths.

今をただ 聞かせて見させて

誰よりも困難だって

思い出して

さあね さあね
不甲斐ないね
君の言葉はキャラメル味でした

期待だけ上がらないで
どうしたってつまんないね
居場所などもうない

手を伸ばすこと あの頃は不器用だった

謝りたいよ もう戻れやしないから

その為に生きていて
声が出せなくたって
